description:
Welcome to the world of dizzying and adrenaline racing! In this game you will face the most dangerous obstacles at a great height. On your way you have to overcome various obstacles, avoid traps and set a new speed record on dangerous tracks.

The game has a huge selection of powerful sports cars. Win races, set new records and fill up your garage with powerful sports cars. And don't forget to upgrade your car to the maximum level!

On each track you will encounter unique obstacles that will try to knock you off the track. Some obstacles can suddenly change your direction of travel, others can stop your car if you are not careful and attentive.

Try to overcome as many obstacles as possible and set your new personal speed record on each track. Prove to everyone who is the King of the Downhill here!

GAME FEATURES:
• Excellent warm-up for dexterity and attentiveness;
• Lots of tracks with varying difficulty;
• Large garage of powerful sports cars;
• Addictive gameplay for all ages;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;
